com.attivio.sdk.client.exposedapi.jmx

Annotation Type JmxReadable


  • @Inherited
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface JmxReadable
    Annotation to apply to a getter method to mark it as a readable attribute in JMX.
